    "body": "Hey @jhay006! \r\n\r\nYou should be able to pass your local solc-js compiler to Truffle by specifying the path to it within your `truffle-config.js` file:\r\n\r\n```\r\nmodule.exports = {\r\n  compilers: {\r\n    solc: {\r\n      version: \"./some/path\"\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n```",
