    "body": "@jhay006 Just a note, if you use `truffle obtain` to install the package, this is not the same as the \"native\" setting. If you use \"native\", Truffle assumes that you have installed solc externally to Truffle through something like `brew` or `apt-get`. See [this doc](https://solidity.readthedocs.io/en/v0.5.11/installing-solidity.html#binary-packages) for more info.",
